				<header><h1>Notes</h1></header>
				Lock ops far arm under yours and sweep them over your back, you roll over your shoulder</br>
				counter to above is for op to pull knee out and sprawl, then you continue to hold their arm while inverted (stalled roll) then spin 180 end up back to back with them face/chest down and you sitting up</br>
				Knee in to the spot between turtled guys leg / arm / chest, poke knee in pointing back towards ops legs, the knee nearest ops head is the one to attach with</p>
